    schema:recipeIngredient "[\"1 lb. ground beef\",\"1 small white onion, diced\",\"3 (15 oz.) cans diced tomatoes with green chiles\",\"2 (15 oz.) cans beans, drained (black beans, kidney beans, a combo, or whatever you like)\",\"2 Tbsp. chili powder\"]";
