# Ordering of the elements should be taken care of by using listItems, but I'm not in the mood to make a bunch of blank nodes
instructions:606DB6E79B3BEC0009000001 rdf:type schema:ItemList;
    mu:uuid "606DB6E79B3BEC0009000001";
    schema:itemListElement "[\"0. In a large stockpot, cook ground beef or turkey over medium-high heat until browned, stirring frequently.  Using a slotted spoon, transfer the cooked beef or turkey to a separate plate and set aside.  Reserve 1 tablespoon of grease in the stockpot, and discard the rest.\",\"1. Add the onion to the stockpot and saute for 4-5 minutes, or until soft.\",\"2. Add remaining ingredients and the cooked beef or turkey to the stockpot, and stir to combine. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to medium-low, cover, and simmer for 10 minutes.\",\"3. Serve immediately, garnished with optional toppings if desired.  Or, store in a sealed container for up to 3 days.\"]".